{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>PodVerse Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ff3838 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #ff3838;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #ff3838;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        .shapes div {\n            position: absolute;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n        }\n        .shape1 { top: 10%; left: 20%; width: 150px; height: 150px; animation: float 5s infinite ease-in-out alternate; }\n        .shape2 { top: 50%; left: 70%; width: 100px; height: 100px; animation: float 7s infinite ease-in-out alternate-reverse; }\n        .shape3 { top: 30%; left: 50%; width: 200px; height: 200px; animation: float 6s infinite ease-in-out; }\n\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0); }\n            100% { transform: translateY(-30px); }\n        }\n\n        .content-section {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .content-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #ff3838;\n        }\n        .podcasts-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .podcast-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .podcast-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .podcast-info h3 {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #ff6b6b;\n        }\n        .podcast-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .listen-button {\n            background-color: #ff3838;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: auto;\n        }\n        .listen-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e02b2b;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #ff6b6b;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 { font-size: 3em; }\n            .hero p { font-size: 1.2em; }\n            .content-section h2 { font-size: 2em; }\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5em; }\n            .hero p { font-size: 1.1em; }\n            .cta-button { padding: 12px 25px; font-size: 1em; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"shapes\">\n            <div class=\"shape1\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape2\"></div>\n            <div class=\"shape3\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <h1>PodVerse Network</h1>\n        <p>Dive into a universe of captivating stories, insightful discussions, and endless entertainment. Your next favorite podcast is just a click away.</p>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Podcasts</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"podcasts\" class=\"content-section\">\n        <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n        <div class=\"podcasts-grid\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ff6b6b/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast 1 Cover\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>The Cosmic Chronicle</h3>\n                    <p>Journey through the galaxies with our hosts as they explore the latest in space and science fiction.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ff8e44/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast 2 Cover\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>Whispers of the Past</h3>\n                    <p>Uncover forgotten histories and intriguing mysteries from around the globe.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/59c173/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast 3 Cover\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>The Daily Grind</h3>\n                    <p>Real talk about modern life, career challenges, and finding balance in a busy world.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/7359c1/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast 4 Cover\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>Articulate Adventures</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the world of art, creativity, and the stories behind the masterpieces.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"background-color: #ffeded;\">\n        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>\n        <p>Connect with fellow listeners, share your favorite episodes, and discover new shows through our vibrant online community.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: #ff3838; color: #ffffff; border: 2px solid #ff3838;\">Sign Up Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 PodVerse Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Made with <span style=\"color: #ff6b6b;\">&#10084;</span> for podcast lovers.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}